Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
model.Reservation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Reservation extends Object implements Serializable
Class representing a reservation with specific attributes such as date interval, price per animal, customer, animals, and comment.
Version:
1.0 - December 2024
Author:
Martin Skovby Andersen, Rasmus Duus Kristensen, Victor Grud Oksen, Victor Sander Marx Hoelgaard
